snippet.title: Devilated Official Trailer
snippet.description:
A game by Trung Cao "Trunks".
Devilated is a brutal first-person shooter with Role-playing elements and complex key-hunting levels. Survive and roast enemies on a journey of violence.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/570950/Devilated/
